| table2_order                   |         2 |    2 |
| table2_order                   |         3 |    2 |
| table2_order                   |         4 |    2 |
| table2_order                   |         5 |    2 |
| 数据库中断前自增值==>          |         6 |    1 |
+--------------------------------+-----------+------+
